sentences: Informal consultations included a discussion of the Secretariat s table compiling existing emission reduction pledges by Annex I parties.
Delegates also addressed the South African proposal ( FCCC/KP/AWG/2009/CRP.3 ), which contains, inter alia , individual targets for Annex I parties, and discussed the underlying criteria.
enb_long_title: Fifth session of the Ad Hoc Working Group on Long-term Cooperative Action under the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change (AWG-LCA 5) and Seventh session of the Ad Hoc Working Group on Further Commitments for Annex I Parties under the Kyoto Protocol (AWG-KP 7)
